      <title>保守党承诺减税、限制移民：宣言概览</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/uk-conservative-manifesto-2024-rishi-sunak-unveils-his-election-promises</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国保守党公布了 2024 年大选宣言，阐述了他们对下一届任期的愿景。]]></description>
